      <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-black uppercase text-dark mb-2">Upgrade Your Plan</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-gray-600 mb-5">
        You've reached the player limit on your current plan. Upgrade to add more players and unlock additional features.
      </p>
